88
00:03:05,687 --> 00:03:07,003
Simon ...

89
00:03:07,038 --> 00:03:09,402
Onde aprendes-te a lutar assim?

90
00:03:09,437 --> 00:03:10,787
Escola hebraica.

91
00:03:10,822 --> 00:03:13,005
♪ Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh ♪

92
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:13,882
♪ Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh ♪

93
00:03:13,917 --> 00:03:15,841
- ♪ ♪ 17
